org.apache.spark.sql.parquet

Class CatalystPrimitiveStringConverter

  • Object
    • parquet.io.api.Converter
      • parquet.io.api.PrimitiveConverter
        • org.apache.spark.sql.parquet.CatalystPrimitiveConverter
          • org.apache.spark.sql.parquet.CatalystPrimitiveStringConverter

  • public class CatalystPrimitiveStringConverter
extends CatalystPrimitiveConverter
    A parquet.io.api.PrimitiveConverter that converts Parquet Binary to Catalyst String. Supports dictionaries to reduce Binary to String conversion overhead.

    Follows pattern in Parquet of using dictionaries, where supported, for String conversion.
